        "action": "Review school exclusion policies and practices in academies",
        "additional_details": "This review should look at:  \r\n \r\n- Existing practices around exclusion, and alternatives to these\r\n- Rates of exclusion, including by ethnicity\r\n- The role of Governors and headteachers in decision-making about exclusions.",
